modName: Tropical Skyrim - Elephants Instead of Mammoths
summary: This replaces the mammoths in Skyrim with elephants for users of tropical Skyrim. I saw 1000 requests for this everywhere so I decided to do it.
descriptionHtml:
This replaces the mammoths in Skyrim with elephants for users of tropical Skyrim. I saw 1000 requests for this everywhere so I decided to do it. Tropical Skyrim is not required for this to work, but the whole point of this mod is to work with tropical Skyrim.

Tropical Skyrim:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33017/?

Credits:
Dogtown1 - Elephant

Other Tropical Skyrim animal replacers:

Werehyena replaces Werewolf: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51499/?
Zebra replaces Horse: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33466/?
author: GendunDrup
